257d09d3-69b2-4af4-aaeb-e0d28e610ada.description: Very difficult hike. The denivelation and the distance are a lot, but the views are awesome. I suggest it to everyone who is in a good shape

9927abba-4efd-4c4a-ad2b-ea0a4766b005.description: This is the Bulgarian mountainer classic! Quite difficult one with very steep hills to climb, but with stunning views. Absolutely recommend for anyone who hasn't done it yet!
